Add interactive dashboard and executive summary

- dashboard.html (295 KB, self-contained Plotly) with 6 sections:
  1. World choropleth of life expectancy 2015
  2. Pairwise Pearson correlation ranking (24 indicators)
  3. Country-level explorer with indicator dropdown + LOWESS
  4. Pearson vs Spearman sensitivity scatter
  5. Longitudinal heatmap of 9 strong correlates x 4 years
  6. Handwashing scatter with bivariate vs multivariate fit lines
- Executive Summary.md (~600 words) — one-page visual brief.
- make_dashboard.py — regenerates the HTML from csv_data/ and the WB API.
- README updated: Start Here block, document table, repo tree, Reproduce.
